name: Depth Of The Ocean
description:
Unlike the land, the ocean exist in multiple dimensions that divide into a series of layers. Based on research, 90% of the ocean is uniformly dark, cold, and under extreme pressure. But still at some point of layers, ocean is the earth's livable habitat.

This is the very first collaboration of me and my husband - Consfunkracy a.k.a GNDHI. He created the sound.
